BRANIFF
SERVICE
HIGHLIGHTS
• New daily round trip service between Dallas-Fort Worth
and Washington (National) gives Braniff eight flights every
business day between the two cities. Six are one-stops
serving National Airport plus two non-stops serving
Dulles.
• Now two additional flights each way between Denver and
Atlanta for a total of four every business day.
• Now four non-stops every business day to
Minneapolis-St. Paul from Dallas-Fort Worth.
• Other new service from Dallas-Fort Worth includes a
midday non-stop to Memphis, afternoon non-stops to
Nashville and New Orleans and additional round trip
flights serving Seattle-Tacoma and Portland.
• Ten non-stops every business day between New
York-Newark and Dallas-Fort Worth.
• New afternoon non-stop from Nashville to Dallas-Fort
Worth makes it a total of three every business day.
• Every hour service from morning to early evening
between Dallas-Fort Worth and Denver, Chicago,
Houston and San Antonio.
• Memphis now has three non-stop round trips every
business day serving Washington (National).
• Now morning and evening non-stop service from Kansas
City to Houston.
Check our schedule for these and other Braniff flights
throughout the U.S. Mainland, Hawaii, Mexico and South
America. Then for reservations call your travel agent or
Braniff International.
